<br>
A few of her wolves stayed at her sides while she had others scouting the area. Themiscrya did had spies ever so often and Alysia was not one to show mercy to anything that gave her a reason to.<br>
<br>
She eventually dismounted outside near the Queen's Hut and nodded to the guard. She looked to her pack and nodded to them to stay behind taking only Scythe and Aeceus with her.<br>
<br>
She entered the hut after giving leave to, and as she overheard the words of Dawn she spoke.<br>
<br>
&quot;Then if I may suggest we go and make things right.&quot;<br>
<br>
